        6/3/2015
    

I've been to this bank to make deposits for personal and business accounts. To be fair, I haven't used any other services (such as talking to a personal banker). However, every time I come to the bank, there is only one or two tellers working. At most I've seen there are three tellers. I expect there to be more when it's a Monday/Friday or beginning of the month. There is an awful smell there too. It might be the air conditioning. All in all, expect to be there for a while on a quick transaction. The reason for two stars is for the service you do get when you are seen. The staff seems friendly.




