        2/9/2013
    








5 check-ins
        


This branch is centrally located just off Main Street in Los Altos.  It's easy to find, it has a drive-up ATM (and another around the corner, also outside), I haven't been yet when there's a wait for a teller, and everyone I've encountered here is friendly and helpful.  I only carry checking and savings accounts with Bank of America due to the fees the bank slaps on all of their accounts and transactions, but I have been very happy with this branch.




