Pretty average for a BoA. I've come here a few times because of location and convenience, but the parking situation is really bizarre and the exit is just as weird. It feels very boxed in, and confusing to get out of if you have to return the same direction you came.The staff is nice but sparse, on a busy day count on having to wait quite a bit if your transaction is outside of ATM-ability because they're so understaffed. Otherwise, everyone is pretty nice, they really could use an update though.




